1
00:00:12,200 --> 00:00:14,530
I was just worrying that His Majesty kept Shen Zhengran imprisoned without executing him,

2
00:00:14,530 --> 00:00:17,360
but the Shen family unexpectedly came knocking on our door to court death.

3
00:00:17,360 --> 00:00:18,130
But Father,

4
00:00:18,500 --> 00:00:20,000
how can we prove to His Majesty

5
00:00:20,000 --> 00:00:21,560
that Shen Luyi forged the late Emperor's edict?

6
00:00:21,560 --> 00:00:23,400
His Majesty values Lu Jingxing so much.

7
00:00:23,400 --> 00:00:24,860
Will he believe our words?

8
00:00:27,960 --> 00:00:29,960
I have the best evidence in my hands.

9
00:00:30,360 --> 00:00:31,160
What is it?

10
00:00:31,630 --> 00:00:33,030
Father, tell me quickly.

11
00:00:34,200 --> 00:00:35,900
The real edict

12
00:00:37,100 --> 00:00:39,030
is right in my hands.

13
00:00:39,700 --> 00:00:42,200
Shen Zhengran held the late Emperor's edict

14
00:00:42,200 --> 00:00:44,100
and was fiercely loyal to the late Emperor.

15
00:00:44,100 --> 00:00:45,760
Yet His Majesty said something like

16
00:00:45,760 --> 00:00:47,230
he valued his loyalty,

17
00:00:47,560 --> 00:00:50,400
and would restore him to his original post if he handed over the edict.

18
00:00:50,400 --> 00:00:53,030
So when I confiscated the Minister's mansion, I found the edict

19
00:00:53,030 --> 00:00:55,160
and secretly took it away.

20
00:00:55,160 --> 00:00:57,160
No wonder Minister Shen cried foul.

21
00:00:57,560 --> 00:00:59,560
It turns out he wasn't hiding the edict.

22
00:00:59,560 --> 00:01:01,000
He really couldn't hand it over.

23
00:01:01,000 --> 00:01:02,300
This way,

24
00:01:02,300 --> 00:01:04,700
His Majesty suspects Minister Shen of hiding the edict,

25
00:01:04,700 --> 00:01:07,630
and Minister Shen suspects His Majesty of playing tricks.

26
00:01:07,630 --> 00:01:08,960
With the ruler and subject suspecting each other,

27
00:01:08,960 --> 00:01:12,330
let's see if Shen Zhengran can still be restored to his post.

28
00:01:12,330 --> 00:01:15,130
Father, you are truly calculating and wise.

29
00:01:15,130 --> 00:01:17,130
I wholeheartedly support His Majesty.

30
00:01:17,130 --> 00:01:20,260
But His Majesty still cares about a sycophant like Shen Zhengran.

31
00:01:20,260 --> 00:01:21,530
Then what am I?

32
00:01:21,530 --> 00:01:22,530
A joke.

33
00:01:22,530 --> 00:01:24,930
But if you take out the edict now,

34
00:01:24,930 --> 00:01:27,730
the fact that the Shen family and Lu Jingxing forged the edict will indeed be exposed,

35
00:01:27,730 --> 00:01:30,130
but you will also be punished by His Majesty, right?

36
00:01:30,130 --> 00:01:31,390
That's easy to handle.

37
00:01:31,430 --> 00:01:33,930
I'll just say I have been searching silently,

38
00:01:33,930 --> 00:01:37,600
and finally found the edict Shen Zhengran hid.

39
00:01:38,830 --> 00:01:42,229
Once I nail Lu Jingxing and the Shen family and make a great contribution,

40
00:01:42,229 --> 00:01:44,890
the Wei family will be full of glory from then on.

41
00:01:45,200 --> 00:01:46,729
You'll be rewarded for reporting it first.

42
00:01:46,729 --> 00:01:49,190
His Majesty might even title you a princess.

43
00:01:49,200 --> 00:01:51,330
Then you can have any husband you want.

44
00:01:57,259 --> 00:01:58,000
Well done.

45
00:02:03,730 --> 00:02:05,860
This forged edict is simply flawless.

46
00:02:06,160 --> 00:02:08,259
Let's go to the palace and hand it to His Majesty,

47
00:02:08,259 --> 00:02:11,390
begging His Majesty to pardon the Shen family's crimes.

48
00:02:19,130 --> 00:02:20,060
Father.

49
00:02:20,430 --> 00:02:21,660
It worked.

50
00:02:21,660 --> 00:02:23,800
Lu Jingxing and Shen Luyi have gone out with the fake edict.

51
00:02:23,800 --> 00:02:25,200
They entered the palace.

52
00:02:26,130 --> 00:02:26,900
Good.

53
00:02:27,260 --> 00:02:28,630
Follow me to the storehouse.

54
00:02:28,630 --> 00:02:30,000
We'll fetch the edict

55
00:02:30,000 --> 00:02:31,200
and enter the palace.

56
00:03:10,660 --> 00:03:12,500
This is the edict left by the late Emperor.

57
00:03:12,500 --> 00:03:15,560
The edict has the late Emperor's personal seal on it.

58
00:03:15,860 --> 00:03:17,300
Once it is taken out,

59
00:03:17,660 --> 00:03:20,000
the fake edict will have nowhere to hide.

60
00:03:27,500 --> 00:03:29,530
Thank you for making this happen, Grand Tutor Wei.

61
00:03:29,530 --> 00:03:31,360
You... you all...

62
00:03:31,360 --> 00:03:32,630
Guards!

63
00:03:32,630 --> 00:03:34,890
Somebody come quickly, there's a thief!

64
00:03:38,900 --> 00:03:41,630
Father, why is no one coming to save us?

65
00:03:41,630 --> 00:03:43,230
You fool, don't you understand?

66
00:03:43,230 --> 00:03:44,829
You fell for their trap.

67
00:03:46,700 --> 00:03:47,700
Husband,

68
00:03:47,700 --> 00:03:49,430
Husband, spare me.

69
00:03:49,430 --> 00:03:51,430
I am your wife.

70
00:03:51,430 --> 00:03:53,430
I am the wife of General Weibei.

71
00:03:53,730 --> 00:03:55,630
I never formally married you.

72
00:03:56,400 --> 00:03:58,160
We never bowed to heaven and earth.

73
00:03:58,160 --> 00:04:00,100
Nor did we consummate the marriage.

74
00:04:00,100 --> 00:04:02,500
I, Lu Jingxing, will only have one wife in this life,

75
00:04:02,500 --> 00:04:03,830
Shen Luyi.

76
00:04:05,960 --> 00:04:07,000
Lu Jingxing,

77
00:04:07,300 --> 00:04:08,900
you can't treat me like this.

78
00:04:18,899 --> 00:04:20,899
The late Emperor's personal edict.

79
00:04:21,829 --> 00:04:23,760
I feel unwell,

80
00:04:24,030 --> 00:04:26,030
and fear I do not have much time left.

81
00:04:26,030 --> 00:04:28,560
Although I have a son living among the people,

82
00:04:28,960 --> 00:04:31,260
he is young and the state would be unstable.

83
00:04:31,260 --> 00:04:33,430
I fear he cannot bear the great responsibility.

84
00:04:33,430 --> 00:04:35,290
My imperial brother, Prince Bao,

85
00:04:35,600 --> 00:04:36,930
is highly intelligent,

86
00:04:37,159 --> 00:04:38,330
versed in civil and military affairs,

87
00:04:38,330 --> 00:04:39,860
and has deeply won my heart.

88
00:04:40,530 --> 00:04:42,800
He is fit to inherit the throne.

89
00:04:43,460 --> 00:04:46,000
I have decided to pass the throne to my brother.

90
00:04:46,000 --> 00:04:48,159
I strip my young son of all his titles.

91
00:04:48,630 --> 00:04:51,360
The Imperial Household Department shall provide for him.

92
00:04:51,360 --> 00:04:53,820
It is enough for him to be a wealthy commoner.

93
00:04:55,400 --> 00:04:56,960
Respect this.

94
00:04:57,800 --> 00:05:01,600
Long live the Emperor!

95
00:05:01,930 --> 00:05:04,260
The late Emperor was immensely kind to me.

96
00:05:04,800 --> 00:05:06,800
I will not fail his trust,

97
00:05:06,800 --> 00:05:08,030
and will govern diligently

98
00:05:08,030 --> 00:05:09,960
to protect the Great Sheng Empire.

99
00:05:11,060 --> 00:05:12,730
Grand Tutor Wei framed loyal officials

100
00:05:12,730 --> 00:05:14,030
and stole the late Emperor's edict.

101
00:05:14,030 --> 00:05:14,900
He intended to rebel,

102
00:05:14,900 --> 00:05:15,960
and the evidence is irrefutable.

103
00:05:15,960 --> 00:05:16,830
Men,

104
00:05:16,830 --> 00:05:18,530
drag Grand Tutor Wei out

105
00:05:18,530 --> 00:05:21,500
and throw him into the death row to await his sentence.

106
00:05:21,500 --> 00:05:22,630
Your Majesty, spare my life!

107
00:05:22,630 --> 00:05:24,660
Have mercy, Your Majesty!

108
00:05:24,930 --> 00:05:26,330
My beloved Minister Shen,

109
00:05:26,330 --> 00:05:27,730
you were wrongly accused.

110
00:05:27,730 --> 00:05:29,130
Your loyalty is commendable.

111
00:05:29,130 --> 00:05:30,160
You are restored to your original post.

112
00:05:30,160 --> 00:05:32,360
Thank you for your grace, Your Majesty.

113
00:05:32,400 --> 00:05:35,200
Shen Luyi, the eldest daughter of Minister Shen,

114
00:05:35,200 --> 00:05:36,460
though a woman,

115
00:05:36,460 --> 00:05:38,030
understands the greater good

116
00:05:38,030 --> 00:05:39,330
and has excellent character.

117
00:05:39,330 --> 00:05:41,330
She has made great contributions this time.

118
00:05:41,330 --> 00:05:43,560
I grant her the title of Princess Yongning.

119
00:05:43,560 --> 00:05:45,760
Thank you for your grace, Your Majesty.

120
00:05:57,330 --> 00:05:59,930
We are finally back.

121
00:06:01,660 --> 00:06:02,360
Let's go.

122
00:06:03,030 --> 00:06:03,830
Let's go home.

123
00:06:11,330 --> 00:06:14,260
I never expected our family could reunite like this.

124
00:06:14,600 --> 00:06:15,760
It's truly a blessing.

125
00:06:15,760 --> 00:06:16,460
Yes.

126
00:06:16,800 --> 00:06:18,400
Let's never separate again.

127
00:06:24,160 --> 00:06:24,860
Sister,

128
00:06:25,300 --> 00:06:27,060
are you waiting for brother-in-law?

129
00:06:27,060 --> 00:06:29,200
You were titled Princess today.

130
00:06:29,400 --> 00:06:31,800
He will definitely come back to celebrate.

131
00:06:34,430 --> 00:06:36,900
Luyi's wedding was too rushed before.

132
00:06:36,900 --> 00:06:38,159
Now that everything is settled,

133
00:06:38,159 --> 00:06:40,630
we must make up for it with a grand wedding.

134
00:06:40,900 --> 00:06:41,760
No need.

135
00:06:41,760 --> 00:06:42,330
Father,

136
00:06:42,700 --> 00:06:44,460
I have already got the best of everything.

137
00:06:44,460 --> 00:06:46,230
Having my family and him,

138
00:06:46,230 --> 00:06:47,200
is enough.

139
00:06:48,200 --> 00:06:49,659
Miss, bad news!

140
00:06:49,659 --> 00:06:50,530
The General,

141
00:06:50,530 --> 00:06:52,390
he's been locked in the death row!

142
00:06:52,900 --> 00:06:53,760
What?

143
00:06:54,000 --> 00:06:54,860
Death row?
